            "title": "The prevalence of antibodies to simian T-cell leukaemia/lymphotropic virus (STLV-I) in non-human primate colonies in Kenya",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "J. M.",
                    "lastName": "Mwenda"
