            "title": "Glucocorticoids, energy metabolites, and immunity vary across allostatic states for plateau side-blotched lizards (Uta stansburiana uniformis) residing in a heterogeneous thermal environment",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Spencer B.",
